# SLO/SLA Dashboard

> Generated: {{ generated_at }}
> Window: {{ window }} days

## Service Health

| Service | Target SLO | Current SLO | Status | Uptime |
|---------|-----------|-------------|--------|--------|
{% for service in services -%}
| {{ service.name }} | {{ service.target_slo }}% | {{ service.current_slo }}% | {% if service.current_slo >= service.target_slo %}{{ green_indicator }}{% elif service.current_slo >= (service.target_slo * 0.9) | round(1) %}{{ yellow_indicator }}{% else %}{{ red_indicator }}{% endif %} | {{ service.uptime }}% |
{% endfor %}

## Error Budget

{% for service in services -%}
### {{ service.name }}
- **Budget window**: {{ window }} days
- **Target**: {{ service.target_slo }}% availability
- **Allowed downtime**: {{ service.error_budget_hours }}h
- **Consumed**: {{ service.error_budget_consumed }}h
- **Remaining**: {{ service.error_budget_remaining }}h
- **Status**: {% if service.error_budget_consumed < (service.error_budget_hours * 0.5) | round(2) %}{{ green_indicator }} Healthy{% elif service.error_budget_consumed < service.error_budget_hours %}{{ yellow_indicator }} Warning{% else %}{{ red_indicator }} Exhausted{% endif %}

{% endfor -%}

## Latency SLOs (p99)

| Service | Target (p99) | Current (p99) | Target (p50) | Current (p50) | Status |
|---------|-------------|--------------|-------------|--------------|--------|
{% for service in services -%}
| {{ service.name }} | {{ service.latency_target_p99 }}ms | {{ service.latency_current_p99 }}ms | {{ service.latency_target_p50 }}ms | {{ service.latency_current_p50 }}ms | {% if service.latency_current_p99 <= service.latency_target_p99 %}{{ green_indicator }}{% elif service.latency_current_p99 <= (service.latency_target_p99 * 1.5) | round(0) %}{{ yellow_indicator }}{% else %}{{ red_indicator }}{% endif %} |
{% endfor %}

## Dependency Health

| Dependency | Type | Status | Notes |
|-----------|------|--------|-------|
{% for dep in dependencies -%}
| {{ dep.name }} | {{ dep.type }} | {% if dep.status == "healthy" %}{{ green_indicator }} Healthy{% elif dep.status == "degraded" %}{{ yellow_indicator }} Degraded{% else %}{{ red_indicator }} Down{% endif %} | {{ dep.notes }} |
{% endfor %}

## Recent Incidents (Last {{ window }} Days)

{% if incidents.len() > 0 -%}
| Date | Service | Severity | Summary | Duration | Status |
|------|---------|----------|---------|----------|--------|
{% for incident in incidents -%}
| {{ incident.date }} | {{ incident.service }} | {% if incident.severity == "critical" %}{{ red_indicator }} Critical{% elif incident.severity == "high" %}{{ yellow_indicator }} High{% else %}{{ green_indicator }} Low{% endif %} | {{ incident.summary }} | {{ incident.duration }} | {{ incident.status }} |
{% endfor -%}
{% else -%}
{{ green_indicator }} No incidents in the last {{ window }} days.
{% endif -%}

## SLO Summary

| Metric | Value |
|--------|-------|
| **Total services tracked** | {{ services.len() }} |
| **Services meeting SLO** | {{ services | filter(attribute="current_slo", op=">=", value=services[0].target_slo) | length }} |
| **Services breaching SLO** | {{ services | filter(attribute="current_slo", op="<", value=services[0].target_slo) | length }} |
| **Active incidents** | {{ incidents | filter(attribute="status", value="active") | length }} |
| **Error budget remaining (aggregate)** | {{ aggregate_error_budget_remaining }}h |

---

**Legend**: {{ green_indicator }} = Healthy | {{ yellow_indicator }} = Warning | {{ red_indicator }} = Critical
